Name: Vintage Tech Hunters
Title: Bohus and Shaun Buy a Jukebox
Desc: During a road trip in California, Bohus and Shaun find a vintage jukebox; local flea markets.
LongDescription: During a road trip in Southern California, Bohus and Shaun find a vintage jukebox in need of repair and take it to Los Angeles to have it restored; in Los Angeles they hunt for vintage tech at local flea markets and an e-waste recycling facility.
